node.text:
During New York Design Week, @suiteny hosted a design conversation with @gamfratesi and GUBI to talk about the story behind the iconic Beetle Chair. See the conversation moderated by @spencercbailey here.
#gubi #gubiofficial #beetlechair #gamfratesi

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by GUBI on September 02, 2021. May be an image of furniture and indoor.

node.text:
The GMG Chaise Longue is perfectly angled for lounging whilst preserving all the streamlined qualities of a mid-century design. 

Image by @katrin_mood for @zrobim_architects
.
.
.
#gubi #gubiofficial #gmgchaiselongue #gretamgrossman #gravitylamp #spacecopenhagen

node.text:
A little ahead of its time in 1975, the modular Pacha Collection is finally coming into its own today.

Architects and designers: @leberrevevaud
Image via @south_hill_home
Featured in @ad_magazine
Photo by @stephanjulliard
.
.
.
#gubi #gubiofficial #pachachair #pierrepaulin

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by GUBI on August 30, 2021. May be an image of table and indoor.

node.text:
The Violin Chair epitomizes GamFratesi’s craftsmanship, creativity, and material understanding.

The musicality of the name resonates with a chair that reflects a musical instrument in its geometry, symmetry and craftsmanship.
.
.
.
#gubi #gubiofficial #violinchair #epictable #gamfratesi #gräshoppalamp #gretagrossman

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by GUBI on August 29, 2021. May be an image of table and indoor.

node.text:
Subtle, organic forms and gentle, diffused light characterize the Stemlite Wall Lamp – a hidden gem from the space race era. The Stemlite was inspired by the strong, organic, yet slender stems that support flower heads in nature.
.
.
.
#gubi #gubiofficial #gubifall2021 #stemlitelamp #billcurry #privatecollection #spacecopenhagen #beetlechair #gamfratesi

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by GUBI on August 27, 2021. May be an image of furniture and indoor.

node.text:
The 9602 Floor Lamp is perfectly suited for casting a gentle ambient light and adding an elegant touch to any interior setting.

Image via @anettehallback
Styling @sundlingkicken
Photo @osmantahir
At @nordiskagalleriet
.
.
.
#gubi #gubiofficial #9602floorlamp #paavotynell

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by GUBI on August 26, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and indoor.

node.text:
GUBI presents the new Midnight Blue edition of the Multi-Lite Pendant.

Timeless and versatile, midnight blue is – as Christian Dior put it – “the only color that can compete with black”. It has the flexibility of a neutral, complementing almost any other shade and introducing a note of refinement to an interior space.
.
.
.
#gubi #gubiofficial #multilite #louisweisdorf

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by GUBI on August 24, 2021. May be an image of table and indoor.

node.text:
The Multi-Lite Collection showcases Louis Weisdorf’s move away from his traditional design style to pursue a more diverse aesthetic. Weisdorf  had a passion for objects that can be changed by the user, involving them in the design process and offering a more dynamic design. 
.
.
.
#gubi #gubiofficial #batchair #beetlechair #epictable #gamfratesi #multilite #louisweisdorf

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by GUBI on August 23, 2021. May be an image of furniture and indoor.

node.text:
The GMG Chaise Longue was designed in 1951 by Greta M. Grossman and with playful elegance it is perfectly angled for lounging. Built in a shape designed for relaxation it mirrors the body’s natural curves while appearing to float above its distinctive slender legs.
.
.
.
#gubi #gubiofficial #gmgchaiselongue #gräshoppalamp #gretamgrossman #stemlitelamp #billcurry

node.text:
With its pure and light curved shape and iconic expression, the timeless F.A. 33 Mirror adds a gentle touch of elegance to any interior style.

Captured at @dimoradellebalze
.
.
.
#gubi #gubiofficial #fa33mirror #gioponti

The Multi-Lite Pendant embraces the golden era of Danish design. The collection reflects Louis Weisdorf’s passion for objects that can be changed by the user, involving them in the design process and offering a more dynamic design.

Image by @kimgrenaa
.
.
.
#gubi #gubiofficial #multilite #louisweisdorf #gubitable

node.text:
Created for the contemporary home, the Wonder Sofa gives the freedom to explore endless combinations of its three simple modules. Create a welcoming retreat that suits your space, needs and personality. ​
​.
.
.
